{"id": "unknown-2026-04-30-004", "date": "2026-04-30", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 4, "week": 18, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["supply_chain_shift"], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.5, "reasons": []}, "title": "MSEs should be key focus in Export Promotion Mission: Piyush Goyal", "content": "Micro and small enterprises (MSEs) and agricultural exports should remain a key focus across all components of the Export Promotion Mission (EPM), Indian Minister of Commerce and Industry Piyush Goyal has said. \nMarket access support should be extended beyond Export Promotion Councils to include other field-level organisations engaged in promoting exports, he said. \nTen EPM components have been operational.", "sources": [{"name": "fibre2fashion_textile", "url": "https://www.fibre2fashion.com/news/textile-news/mses-should-be-key-focus-in-export-promotion-mission-piyush-goyal-310012-newsdetails.htm", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "unknown-2026-04-30-005", "date": "2026-04-30", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 4, "week": 18, "weekday": "Thu"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["cotton_price", "order_visibility", "earnings"], "sentiment": {"label": "negative", "score": -0.5, "keywords": ["pressure"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.75, "reasons": ["涉及財報"]}, "title": "ICE cotton eases on stronger US dollar, profit booking", "content": "ICE cotton futures eased as a stronger US dollar reduced export competitiveness, while profit-taking followed recent multi-month highs after a sustained rally.\nPlanting progress remained steady, adding mild pressure to prices in the near term.\nHowever, dry weather in Texas, geopolitical tensions, and strength in crude oil and grains provided underlying support, limiting downside risks.", "sources": [{"name": "fibre2fashion_textile", "url": "https://www.fibre2fashion.com/news/textile-news/ice-cotton-eases-on-stronger-us-dollar-profit-booking-310013-newsdetails.htm", "type": "rss"}]}
